17:18.907 --> 17:24.853
Both of these things are signs that speak to the scope and strength of this kingdom, that this kingdom is an unending kingdom.

17:25.874 --> 17:30.739
Like the scepter, the sign of your power is going to pass on from generation to generation without end.

17:32.621 --> 17:33.282
It's powerful.

17:34.463 --> 17:37.106
Even this line about the

