It's the speaking of the fertility, most likely that's the image that's referring to the fertility of the kingdom, that he's always going to be able to pass that fertility on from one king to the next.

17:56.125 --> 17:58.669
That a king will always sit on this throne from this family.

17:59.410 --> 18:01.413
It'll be strong, it'll be an enduring kingdom.

18:02.975 --> 18:05.458
And actually early, the near history

18:06.562 --> 18:08.605
The early years have seemed fulfilled naturally.

