They would bless the families of the earth that goes back to the Garden of Eden.

20:34.511 --> 20:42.059
The Adam and Eve, their whole goal, their whole command was to be fruitful, multiply, which actually expand the garden until it covers the earth.

20:43.881 --> 20:45.803
This is what Jesus is doing now.

20:47.525 --> 20:51.890
Growing his kingdom until it covers the earth, Israel as a nation,

20:52.642 --> 20:56.025
was always a shadow of the fulfillment that's found in the church.

20:57.387 --> 20:59.189
God is calling all peoples to Himself.

